    "SVO: Subject + Verb + Object — NEVER change this order in English",
    "He/She/It ke saath ALWAYS verb+s/es (not for I/You/We/They)",
    "Questions mein Do/Does ko pehle laao — verb base form mein rahega",
    "Negative mein don't/doesn't use karo — verb NEVER gets 's' after doesn't",
    "Articles: 'a' (consonant sound), 'an' (vowel sound), 'the' (specific)",
    "Frequency adverbs main verb se PEHLE aate hain (AFTER is/am/are)",
    "Possessives noun se PEHLE aate hain — My book, His car, Their house",
    "Object pronouns verb ke BAAD: She calls ME (not I)",
    "WH word + do/does + subject + V1 — exact word order mat bhoolna",
    "Never say 'Me go' or 'He don't' — common Hindi speaker errors!"
